{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the accuracy of an NER system depends on the quality and coverage of the training data, as well as the complexity of the language and the types of entities we want to recognize\".",
    "In resource-poor languages, where digital resources are limited, NER helps improve search and retrieval systems.",
    "By accurately identifying named entities, search engines can provide more relevant results to users.",
    "For example, a user searching for information about a specific person or location can benefit from NER in retrieving precise and targeted results.",
    "NER is valuable for cross-lingual applications [23], [24], where information needs to be transferred or aligned across different languages."
  ]
}